text: eyata firavun (ovunta) “obata ma anumætiya laba dimata perama oba (musa, harun adinge deviyan vana) ohuva visvasa kalehuya. niyata vasayenma mema nagaravasinva eyin pitamam kara hærimata oba (musa samaga ekkasu vi) kala kumantranayaki me. .(mema kumantranaye phalavipaka) itamat ikmanin oba dæna gannehuya”
